title: Default Sorting Order
text: If no sorting order is specified, the default is to sort ascending (earliest to latest)

title: Specifying Sorting Option
text: The ASC sorting option will sort whatever is being ordered in ascending order with the earliest dates first.

title: Specifying Sorting Option
text: The DESC sorting option will sort whatever is being ordered in descending order with the latest dates first.

title: Sorting Order Syntax
text: CURRENT is not a valid sort order syntax.
